headline: Mondelz Global LLC Expands Voluntary Recall of 2 SKUs of CHIPS AHOY! Baked Bites Brookie in the US
summary: EAST HANOVER, N.J., Dec. 30, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Mondelz Global LLC announced today an expansion of its December 24, 2025 voluntary recall in the United States of CHIPS AHOY! Baked Bites Brookie. This expansion includes one additional code date (10MAY2026) and two additional UPCs of product pouches inside the recalled carton units of CHIPS AHOY! Baked Bites Brookie. This voluntary recall is being conducted because of an incorrect mixing process that resulted in the formation of small corn
